# user-service

User Service is an API for user management.

## User collection [/users?limit={limit}&offset={offset}]

### List All Users within the organization [GET]

+ Parameters
    + limit (number, optional) - the page size limit (20 is a max value);
    + offset (number, optional) - the page offset;

+ Response 200 (application/json)

